<br>
::An advisor walks into the room with almost a dozen little cute girls aged from 6 to 12 mostly. They all bow and stand. The advisor speaks out to Persephone:: Your highness, the young pupils are here for their lessons.<br>
<br>
::Persephone smacks her hand on her forehead and turns to Hades:: I nearly forgot. These are the girls I'm teaching to be my priestesses and yours. They're learning how to bring agriculture to the Underworld. ::The girls look at Hades a bit nervously, this being the first time seeing him in person. A little girl at the age of three or four looks at Hades in a very frightened way. She then squeezes her hands and fidgets in her spot and begins crying in fear::<br>
<br>
Awww, poor sweety ::Persephone stands and walks over to the group with her arms open. The little girl runs with her little legs into Persephone's arms. Persephone picks her up and holds her close as the little girl clings to her sniffling with her little dirty-blonde head on her shoulder:: Don't cry little Porsha, big ole Hades is not going to hurt you. Looks back at Hades and smiles, she speaks to him with her mind ~I know you much look domineering as you are king of the dead, but must you frighten little children?~ her soft laughs ring through his ears and she turns back to the pupils::<br>
<br>
Today young ladies, I'm going to teach you how and where to plan the seed in Tartarus ::the girls moan and the oldest one speaks out:: But can't we go to the Elysian  fields you highness?  ::Persephone smiles:: No Adrienne, we've already learned how to grow things there. Besides, Tartarus does not have any agriculture, and we must feed them too. Come along now class. ::Persephone leads the way out of the throne room with the rest of the girls following behind. Little Porsha stares at Hades extremely shyly with her thumb in her mouth as Persephone carries her out of the room::<br>
<br>
*~*Persephone/Queen of the Underworld*~* <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.showPrevMessage?topicID=196.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.showNextMessage?topicID=196.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=196.topic&index=12><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/blueMoon/addReply.jpg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.emailToFriend?topicID=196.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.threadControl?topicID=196.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/blueMoon/deleteThread.jpg border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=196.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=196.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub11.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="amazonsuniteamazonsunitescrollboard">Amazons Unite Scroll Board<option value="amazonsunitefrm37">The Mythical Odyssey Forum<option value="amazonsunitefrm23">The Olympian Gods<option value="amazonsunitefrm15">Black Sea Tavern and Inn<option val